        "text_block_LAirjJ": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h5><em>STEP 1: PREP</em></h5><p>Apply the product onto dry hair. Focus on the roots, as this area benefits most from added lift and volume.</p><p><a href=\"/products/schwarzkopf-osis-dust-it-mattifying-volume-powder-10g\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Schwarzkopf OSiS Dust It Mattifying Volume Powder 10g\"><strong>Try the Schwarzkopf OSiS Dust It Mattifying Volume Powder.</strong></a></p><h5><em>STEP 2: STYLE</em></h5><p>Use your fingers or a comb to distribute the product evenly, ensuring that it penetrates well at the base of your hair. This technique will help create a fuller appearance and enhance your overall hairstyle.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": ""
          }
        }
