        "text_block_WTNFar": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h5><em>STEP 1: PREP</em></h5><p>Start by applying a heat protector to shield your hair from damage.</p><p><a href=\"/products/davines-this-is-a-primer-for-natural-shine-anti-humidity-bodifying-effect\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Davines This is a Primer: For Natural Shine, Anti-Humidity, Bodifying Effect\"><strong>Try the Davines This Is A Primer.</strong></a></p><h5><em>STEP 2: STYLE</em></h5><p>Use a volumizing hair tool like a hot air styler to lift your roots and add volume.</p><p><a href=\"/products/tymo-volumizer-hot-brush-hc-300\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TYMO Volumizer Hot Brush HC-300\"><strong>Try the TYMO Volumizing Hot Brush.</strong></a></p><h5><em>STEP 3: FINISH</em></h5><p>Give the roots an extra lift with a texturing powder.</p><p><a href=\"/products/davines-this-is-a-texturizing-dust-for-instant-volume\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Davines This is a Texturizing Dust: For Instant Volume\"><strong>Try the Davines This is a Texturizing Dust.</strong></a></p>",
            "button_label": "",
