        "text_block_wVAMri": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h5><em>STEP 1: PREP</em></h5><p>Start with 2-3 pumps, depending on your hair type and length. Rub between your palms and finger pads to warm it.</p><p><a href=\"/products/davines-oi-oil-absolute-beautifying-potion-with-roucou-oil\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Davines OI Oil: Absolute Beautifying Potion with Roucou Oil\"><strong>Try the Davines OI Oil.</strong></a></p><h5><em>STEP 2: STYLE</em></h5><p>Distribute evenly on the lengths and ends of dry or damp hair. Make sure to avoid roots and scalp.</p>",
