            "enable_image": false,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h5><em>STEP 1: PREP</em></h5><p>Apply a lightweight styling product with built-in heat protection on damp hair, focusing on mid-lengths to ends for hold and texture.</p><p><a href=\"/products/schwarzkopf-osis-grip-extreme-hold-mousse-200ml\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Schwarzkopf OSiS Grip Extreme Hold Mousse 200ml\"><strong>Try the Schwarzkopf OSiS Grip Extreme Hold Mousse.</strong></a></p><h5><em>STEP 2: STYLE</em></h5><p>After drying your hair all the way, use a curling iron, wrapping small sections around the barrel. Hold for a few seconds and release for perfectly defined curls.</p><p><a href=\"/products/tymo-rota-ionic-rotating-curling-iron-hc-501\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TYMO Rota Ionic Rotating Curling Iron HC-501\"><strong>Try the TYMO Rota Ionic Rotating Curling Iron.</strong></a></p><h5><em>STEP 3: FINISH</em></h5><p>Spray from a 30 cm distance in short bursts for long-lasting yet invisible, strong hold.</p><p><a href=\"/products/schwarzkopf-silhouette-super-hold-hairspray-500ml\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Schwarzkopf Silhouette Super Hold Hairspray 500ml\"><strong>Try the Schwarzkopf Silhouette Super Hold Hairspray.</strong></a></p>",
